Computer version of Air hockey - a game where two players play against each other 
on a low-friction table. Air hockey requires an air-hockey table, 
two player-held strikers, and a puck. 


To install on Ubuntu, Debian run:

    sudo apt-get install g++
    sudo apt-get install libsdl2-dev
    sudo apt-get install libsdl2-mixer-dev
    sudo apt-get install libsdl2-image-dev
    sudo apt-get install libsdl2-ttf-dev

Then run "make" inside of game directory.
